StarkNet Hardhat plugin already supports the latest Cairo v0.4.2. 🥳 

To use it, just set the version in your hardhat.config.js file.
```
module.exports = {
  ...
  cairo: {
    // Defaults to "latest"
    version: "0.4.2"
  }
  ...
};
```

https://www.npmjs.com/package/@shardlabs/starknet-hardhat-plugin

Also, you can use our dockerized cairo cli in your projects (README.md will be updated with instructions):
https://hub.docker.com/repository/docker/shardlabs/cairo-cli
https://github.com/Shard-Labs/cairo-cli-docker

